asset.hookText: Architecture Urban combines style with function. Each bag is expertly crafted using environmentally friendly Nüwa® fabric and a traditional Napa leather trim, resulting in a casual yet refined look. Through smart design, the collection reflects the multi-functionality that is at the core of the Victorinox heritage by offering versatile designs, multi-purpose organization and multiple carrying options.
